id: pmc-078v
title: Align CI+release workflows with peer pm-* packages (Node 22 + Bun)
description: Bumped Node 20 -> 22 and added oven-sh/setup-bun@v2.2.0 to .github/workflows/ci.yml and .github/workflows/release.yml so pm-changelog matches the toolchain used by every other pm-* package.
