close_reason: Closed via pm update
body: "pm-changelog ci.yml and release.yml were on Node 20 with no Bun setup; every peer pm-* package (pm-web, pm-graph, pm-todos, pm-csv, pm-gantt-chart, pm-github, pm-jira, pm-linear, pm-slack, pm-slack-standup, pm-starter, pm-ts-starter, pm-beads, all five pm-preset-*) is on Node 22 + setup-bun@v2.2.0. Aligned the two workflow files. The release job itself is unchanged otherwise; daily cron, npm publish, GitHub release, and pm-changelog-driven CHANGELOG generation all still run as before."
